transcript.content: Hello, this is Anna calling from City Library. I'm just following up to let you know that the book you requested, 'The Art of Storytelling', is ready for you to pick up at your convenience. Please let me know if you have any other questions!
Who's the author of that book?
The author of the book 'The Art of Storytelling' is John Doe. Please let me know if you need any other information about the book or your library account.
Uh, yeah, when can I come pick it up?
You can come pick up the book anytime during our regular library hours, which are Monday through Friday, 9am to 6pm. Would you like me to hold the book for you until a specific day?
Uh, yeah, just talk tomorrow. I'll be there tomorrow.

Okay, great. I've noted that you'll be picking up the book tomorrow. We'll have it ready for you when you come by. Please let me know if there's anything else I can assist you with. I hope you have a wonderful rest of your day!
